{"about_the_game":"<strong>A true idle RPG with roguelite and multiplayer elements.</strong><br>Made for playing (on a second screen) while doing something else.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695110/extras/IFI_Gameplay.gif?t=1733324245\" /><br><br>This is not a clicker game! Start your adventure and idle for a few minutes or a few hours.<br>It's up to you how active (or idle) you want to play.<br><br>Build and customize your own character, level up, gather gear, and create your own unique build.<br>Your build will decide which monsters you can farm for resources. Each build will be very good at gathering a certain resource type, but it will be nearly impossible to gather other resource types. You'll have to trade with other players to get the other resources you need.<br><br>Trading with other players on the auction house will be a huge part of the game. You'll need to trade to get all the resources you need for crafting.<br>In the future I will also add a Clan and Raid system.<br><br>100% Free to Play Forever - No annoying ads or pop-ups, no pay-to-win!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733324245","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695110/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733324245","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695110/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733324245","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695110/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733324245","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>A true idle RPG with roguelite and mul